#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is &kmymoney;?"
msgstr "Kaj je &kmymoney;?"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; is a personal finance manager by &kde;. It enables users to keep "
"careful track of their personal finances by providing a broad array of "
"financial features and tools."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; je upravitelj osebnih financ pri &kde;. Uporabnikom omogoča "
"skrbno spremljanje svojih osebnih financ s širokim naborom finančnih funkcij "
"in orodij."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "The principal goals of the project are:"
msgstr "Glavni cilji projekta so:"

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "Feature Parity"
msgstr "Pariteta funkcij"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; intends to provide all important features found in the "
"commercially available personal finance managers. Although every release of "
"&kmymoney; gets closer and closer to that goal, there is still work to be "
"done."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; namerava zagotoviti vse pomembne funkcije, ki jih najdete v "
"komercialno dostopnih upraviteljih osebnih financ. Čeprav je vsaka izdaja "
"&kmymoney; vse bližje temu cilju, je treba še delati."

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ease of Use"
msgstr "Enostavnost uporabe"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; strives to be the easiest open source personal finance manager to "
"use, especially for the non-technical user."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; si prizadeva biti najlažji odprtokodni upravljalnik osebnih "
"financ za uporabo, zlasti za netehnične uporabnike."

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Correctness"
msgstr "Pravilnost"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Based on tried and tested double entry accounting principles, &kmymoney; "
"ensures that your finances are kept in correct order."
msgstr ""
"Na podlagi preizkušenih dvostavnih računovodskih načel &kmymoney; "
"zagotavlja, da so vaše finance v pravilnem redu."

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "What &kmymoney; is not"
msgstr "Kaj &kmymoney; ni"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As a personal finance manager, &kmymoney; is not intended to support the "
"needs of a business. A small business might find sufficient functionality to "
"use &kmymoney;, but features such as accounts-receivable and accounts-"
"payable are not directly supported. The larger the business, the less likely "
"it is to find &kmymoney; will meet its financial management needs. Most if "
"not all the data needed for a small business, such as for reports for audit "
"and taxation purposes is present, but may need to be extracted using various "
"reports and then processed and assembled into the required formats. In "
"addition, it would be possible to create client, supplier, document, or "
"other features through plugins."
msgstr ""
"Kot upravljalnik osebnih financ &kmymoney; ni namenjen podpori potrebam "
"podjetja. Majhno podjetje lahko najde dovolj funkcionalnosti za uporabo "
"&kmymoney;, vendar funkcionalnosti, kot so terjatve in obveznosti, niso "
"neposredno podprte. Večje kot je podjetje, manj verjetno je, da bo "
"&kmymoney; zadovoljil vaše potrebe po finančnem upravljanju. Večina, če ne "
"vsi podatki, potrebni za mala podjetja, na primer za poročila za revizijske "
"in davčne namene, so prisotni, vendar jih bo morda treba ekstrahirati z "
"različnimi poročili ter nato obdelati in sestaviti v zahtevane formate. "
"Poleg tega bi bilo mogoče ustvariti odjemalca, dobavitelja, dokumenta ali "
"druge funkcije prek vtičnikov."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; is not simply a clone of any of the commercially available "
"personal finance programs. Although many of the features present in "
"&kmymoney; can be found in other similar applications, &kmymoney; strives to "
"present an individual and unique view of your finances."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; ni preprosto klon katerega koli od komercialno dostopnih osebnih "
"finančnih programov. Čeprav veliko funkcionalnosti v &kmymoney; lahko "
"najdete tudi v drugih podobnih aplikacijah, si &kmymoney; prizadeva "
"predstaviti individualen in edinstven pogled na vaše finance."

